Le auto comunicano con CAR2X installata in oltre due milioni di Volkswagen

Di Mauro Notarianni

29 Ott 2025

<img 
                                        fetchpriority="high" 
                                        width="741" 
                                        height="486" 
                                        class="entry-thumb" 
                                        src="https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/CAR2X-741x486.jpg" srcset="https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/CAR2X-741x486.jpg 741w,   https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/CAR2X-50x34.jpg 50w" sizes="(max-width: 741px) 100vw, 741px" 
